  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No one can win against Russia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Russian President Vladimir Putin has said that no western country that boasts of being world powers can defeat Russia in the battlefield.",
        "Russian President Putin accuses that the Western countries, which claim to be world powers, are continuously taking various measures against Russia, and that they have forgotten the Russian-Ukraine peace talks.",
        "Responding to the statements made by Western countries including the United States at the recently concluded 'G7' summit, the Russian President has expressed the following comments.",
        "Russian President Vladimir Putin has further clarified that the Russian army is ready for war at any time with the army of any country that boasts of being world powers."
      ],
